TriggerLogic.Name: obj
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: WG.MissionObjective = "Enemy units are scattered across a tropical achepelago, in the midst of a battle between two rival factions. They will be preoccupied fighting each other and you will be able to mine plenty of metal from the central islands before they notice you. We hope it will be safe for you to make a base in the east of the southern island. \n\nEstablish our camp and await further orders."

TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr:
local text = "Units are massing on either side and it looks like the next battle will be on the central islands. It might help to retreat back to the southern island, but don't miss out on reclaiming the metal left over in the shipwrecks from the sea battles."
WG.NewMissionObjective(text)

local text = "Our intelligence suggests the core in the north island will destroy the revolution in the south using flying fortresses. You'd better get ready - after crushing the revolution they will come for you. Protect yourself and destroy the three enemy aircraft plants on the north island to complete your mission."
WG.NewMissionObjective(text)
